":"originman","category":"robot","pathSegment":"humanoid","slug":"originman","title":{"en":"OriginMan","zh":"OriginMan"},"tagline":{"en":"An open humanoid robot subject built around ROS2, embodied intelligence, and hands-on development.","zh":"围绕 ROS2、具身智能与动手开发的人形机器人主题课程。"},"description":{"en":"OriginMan is a future-oriented desktop humanoid robot project. Learners move from system understanding to setup practice and guided operation through a structured sequence of courses.","zh":"OriginMan 是一个面向未来的桌面人形机器人项目，学习者将从系统认知走向配置实践与操作应用。"},"heroMedia":{"type":"image","src":"/assets/courses/originman/originman-1.png"},"heroEyebrow":{"en":"Robot Subject","zh":"机器人主题"},"pathLabel":{"en":"Humanoid Robots","zh":"人形机器人"},"pathDescription":{"en":"Courses focused on humanoid setup, motion systems, and interactive behaviors.","zh":"聚焦人形机器人搭建、运动系统与交互行为的课程体系。"},"courses":[{"id":"originman-overview-course","slug":"overview","title":{"en":"Overview","zh":"概览"},"summary":{"en":"Start with the project philosophy, intelligent platform architecture, and the complete OriginMan hardware profile.","zh":"从项目理念、智能平台架构与硬件能力开始建立整体认知。"},"access":"open","duration":{"en":"15 min","zh":"15 分钟"},"lessons":[{"id":"originman-home","slug":"lesson-1","title":{"en":"OriginMan Overview","zh":"OriginMan 概览"},"summary":{"en":"Explore the open-source philosophy, intelligent platform stack, and full hardware specification of OriginMan.","zh":"了解 OriginMan 的开源理念、智能平台架构与完整硬件规格。"},"duration":{"en":"15 min","zh":"15 分钟"}}]},{"id":"originman-quick-start-course","slug":"quick-start","title":{"en":"Quick Start","zh":"快速开始"},"summary":{"en":"Boot, connect, and run the first guided OriginMan workflow.","zh":"完成开机、连接与第一条 OriginMan 受引导的工作流。"},"access":"edu","duration":{"en":"18 min","zh":"18 分钟"},"lessons":[{"id":"originman-quick-start","slug":"lesson-1","title":{"en":"Quick Start Walkthrough","zh":"快速开始实操"},"summary":{"en":"Learn the first connection, startup confirmation, and basic motion demo with OriginMan.","zh":"学习 